 she...? A-anyway, how was work? Were you busy?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event10-06-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Insanely busy! All these kids came in just after they finished their club activities. I thought they were going to totally clean out all the icecreams and juice~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event10-06-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I was stuck in the back restocking everything, but the boxes were so heavy... My ankles hurt, and my shoulders are all stiff~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event10-06-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"O-oh, in that case I'll rub your shoulders ... You're right, they're really stiff.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event10-06-033","volum